This paper primarily focuses on the security and privacy concerns of big data stored in the cloud, which falls under the category of "cs.CR" (Cryptography and Security). The paper also discusses the clustering of unstructured big data, which can be categorized under "cs.DB" (Databases) and "cs.IR" (Information Retrieval). Additionally, the paper presents an approach for a secure cloud-based semantic search system, which can be classified under "cs.CY" (Computers and Society) and "cs.SE" (Software Engineering).
